title: 272 - Crime Stats
description: Are you a problem solver? Do you complete what you started? In this episode, the guys discuss being solution-oriented and fixing areas in your life that need improving or things that need completion around the house. A lot of us waste time and the numerous opportunities that life gives us. Instead, we need to take Karl’s advice to, “Put your head down and focus on expanding your value so that you can cover 10 years of growth in 6 months.”
